## Data Attribution

This software processes data from NASA's Voyager 1 spacecraft. The underlying 
scientific data remains in the public domain and is provided by:

- NASA Jet Propulsion Laboratory (JPL)
- NASA Space Physics Data Facility (SPDF)  
- NASA Planetary Data System (PDS)

Users of this software should cite appropriate NASA data sources in any 
publications or research derived from the analysis tools provided herein.

## Acknowledgments

This project acknowledges the remarkable achievements of the NASA Voyager mission
team and the decades of engineering excellence that enable continued scientific
discovery in interstellar space.